name: We are all the same
description: I started to learn Arduino in 2016. The further I learned about it the more I see Arduinos  in kind. it does what was written in it until it broke or been unplugged. Humans seem to have better choices in this case. But still we wake up every day and trying to live under expectations. So whats the difference? We are all the same. We work for a better tomorrow under the capitalism.
